{"tid":491220,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"而家既燒味飯根本食唔到滿足既感覺....","createTime":"2017-12-06T09:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T13:56:59.000Z","uid":72608,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"28155a06c8614ad24affff4dcade24d9ac1c00c6","tid":491220,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"以前食燒味飯,D燒味同飯既份量係好match,D燒味質素仲好高<br />\n<br />\n而家D燒味...叉燒睇運..多數都伏..燒腩比較穩陣<br />\n<br />\n嗌雞/鴨,D燒味佬就切D冇肉得骨同皮既位比你...或者切隻雞翼比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完根本就冇滿足既感覺..反而有種失落既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我寧願燒味飯加價加到4X蚊一盒,但係D料夠滿足起碼啖啖肉令人飽肚<br />\n<br />\n2X蚊3X蚊燒味雙拼飯,每一次買每一次失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解香港燒味界會變成咁....唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76c1e2552c070ed3488bf4dadd0d8b59ccb04bb","tid":491220,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/175812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F175812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d22a4c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最x平，仲賣緊15蚊<br />\n好滿意"},{"pid":"0d74fab378cddc8ce0209e1cc15c35df2a9f4ca3","tid":491220,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/175812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F175812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d22a4c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最x平，仲賣緊15蚊<br />\n好滿意</blockquote><br />\n仲做緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcf18a730f27ab8cb58